Name: Coffee
Description: Richly-flavored coffee made using complex processes such as grinding and drip filtration.

Name: Tea
Description: High-quality tea leaves have been used to brew this tea. Has a rich fragrance.

Name: Juice
Description: Large and full Sunsettias have been hand-juiced to make this delicious sweet-and-sour extract.

Name: Milk
Description: Milk brought in from specific supply channels. The mouthfeel is incredibly smooth, and the aftertaste is sweet.

Name: Caramel
Description: This boiled syrup has a thick texture and rich sweetness.

Name: Lemon
Description: This vibrantly colored fruit has an intense sourness that can produce some unexpected results.

Name: Mint
Description: Freshly picked leaves that can be used to add a cooling taste.

Name: Fizzy Water
Description: A liquid that bubbles over. It has no taste, but its mouthfeel packs a punch!

Name: Cocoa Paste
Description: Processed from cocoa fruit. Its unique aroma can be used to add a rich flavor to the drink.

Name: "Evermotion Mechanical Painting"
Description: A gift from a "dreamer" from Fontaine. It appears to be an exquisitely-made furnishing with some hidden functions.

Name: Windblume Gift
Description: A gift box that you can obtain during the Windblume Festival. Before you open it, you cannot know what's inside, but it shouldn't be anything particularly heavy...

Name: "Maintenance Mek" Salvaged Parts
Description: Disassemble "Maintenance Meks" you have caught to obtain usable materials.
A mysterious book...
Seems to be a mysterious companion...

Name: Fantasia Flowers
Description:
Paper flowers with a peculiar appearance, they are souvenirs earned by putting in passionate performances in the "fantasia."
Can be used to select Wondrous Boons, Mystery Caches, and Brilliant Blessings in the Imaginarium Theater.
This seems to be a mysterious recipe...

Name: Special Furnishing Gift (I)
Description: A special gift you obtained during Lantern Rite, containing a most excellent furnishing for the Realm Within...

Name: Special Furnishing Gift (II)
Description: A special gift you obtained during Lantern Rite, containing a most excellent furnishing for the Realm Within...

Name: Unexpectedly Adopted Fantastic Feline
Description: You met an unexpected guest during the Furball Fortress trial period and adopted a cat as a result. Analysis indicates that it seems to get along with you...

Name: Glittering Finch Coins
Description:
Commemorative currency obtained from playing Bing-Bang Finchball. Made using a glittering golden material, like crystal-clear honey candy.
Perhaps on some level, having finchy coins is a quantitative form of expression of your love for Finches?
Exchange these with Basima the Fifth during "Bing-Bang Finchball" for prizes.

Name: Reunion EXP
Description: Reach specific Reunion EXP breakpoints to claim Reunion Gifts rewards during Stellar Reunion

Name: Special Recipe Gift
Description: It seems to contain a mysterious surprise recipe. Just looking at the magnificent packaging, it's gotta be quality stuff...

Name: Special Furnishing Gift
Description: It seems to contain a mysterious furnishing for the Serenitea Pot. Just looking at the magnificent packaging, it's gotta be quality stuff...

Name: Mysterious Gift
Description: A gift gained from playing games at the Mikawa Flower Festival. It appears to be an exquisitely-made furnishing...
